    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wood paneling on interior walls, usually floor to ceiling; as a rule enriched by carving, gilding, painting, or sometimes inlaying.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
